summaries.short: As Santa prepares to name his successor, Candy readies for her calling as the next Claus.
summaries.full: As the citizens of the North Pole eagerly await the announcement of Santa’s successor, Candy prepares for her calling – while continuing to clash with family and friends. Later, as a shocking revelation sends Santa Inc. reeling, Mrs. Claus makes a surprising decision, and Jingle Jim learns a saucy secret.

titles.short: Cracks in the Peppermint Ceiling Part 1
titles.full: Cracks in the Peppermint Ceiling Part 1

summaries.short: Still reeling from the announcement of Santa’s successor, Candy attempts to unite the workers of the North Pole around a common cause.
summaries.full: After getting some advice from an old friend – and spending some time behind bars – Candy embarks on a mission to make amends with everyone she trampled on her way to the top. Meanwhile, Devin struggles to adjust to his new normal, while the employees of Santa Inc. rally around a common cause: their hatred of jolly St. Nick.

summaries.short: Santa’s birthday festivities are cut short as tensions between Candy and her inner circle escalate. Later, Devin performs a good deed, and Mrs. Claus faces her demons.
summaries.full: As the big man’s birthday nears, an increasingly cunning Candy prepares to roast her rivals. But just when it seems like Santa might finally name his successor, a shocking turn of events shakes up the competition. Meanwhile, friction with friends and family threatens to put a damper on the festivities.

titles.short: Cracks in the Peppermint Ceiling Part 2
titles.full: Cracks in the Peppermint Ceiling Part 2

summaries.short: As Christmas draws closer, Candy rallies her entire crew for a final chance to stick it to Santa.
summaries.full: As the holiday season nears, Candy and her crew make plans for Christmas – and a fa-la-la-la-labor strike. Then, after a fateful run-in with Junior, Candy considers the consequences of her actions – but will that dampen her Christmas cheer?

summaries.short: Junior’s arrival in the South Pole threatens Candy’s ascent to the top of Santa’s list. As Cookie and Goldie find a new friend in Mrs. Claus, Craig crumbles at home.
summaries.full: After Santa extends an invitation to the South Pole, Candy’s attempts to bro out with the Board are thwarted by the arrival of Junior – who will do anything to sleigh his way to the top of Santa’s list. Meanwhile, Cookie and Goldie bond with a bored Mrs. Claus, and Craig crumbles at home.

summaries.short: Unsure of her future with Santa Inc., Candy must decide if she should hop on a golden opportunity with Easter Enterprises or stay loyal to Santa.
summaries.full: Still reeling from the aftermath of her ho-ho-horrible speech, Candy receives a job offer from Easter Enterprises that she’d be hopping mad not to take. Meanwhile, Cookie tries to catch up on lost sleep, while Santa relives his college days with a little help from Devin.
